Season two of Queen B’s much anticipated reality show Being Bonang will hit the screens on Friday the 4th of May. Fans can look forward to a lot of excitement on the new season especially if the teaser shared by Bonang is anything to go by. We know that AKA didn’t take the breakup too well, but it appears neither did Bonang and the teaser gives fans a glimpse into how she dealt with it. AKA CAN’T GET OVER BONANG “Let me tell you how I dealt with my breakup….you cry and cry and cry and cry….,” Bonang said. Although she fears she might never find a decent guy, she reveals that going back to AKA is not an option. Watch the teaser below:  